don't turn Jell-O on me now.

11:02.096 --> 11:04.359
We are not giving up.
And we can't let my dad win.

11:04.402 --> 11:06.709
But your dad is saying
the exact same thing,

11:06.753 --> 11:08.406
because you're both
so stubborn.

11:08.450 --> 11:10.147
I'm not stubborn.

11:10.191 --> 11:12.933
