No, I'm passionate.

11:19.635 --> 11:22.159
And you're the one
whose ideas he's always
stomping all over.

11:22.203 --> 11:23.726
He treats you
like a doormat.

11:23.770 --> 11:26.555
As he has since
our first awkward handshake.

11:26.598 --> 11:28.383
Which he mocked.

11:28.426 --> 11:32.909
