"He-e-y, fish hand guy!"

11:34.650 --> 11:36.565
Well, you may be okay with it,
but I'm not.

11:36.608 --> 11:37.740
Now, come on.
Let's take a picture.

11:37.784 --> 11:39.133
Put your arm around me.
[ Sighs ]

11:39.176 --> 11:40.569
Vanessa!
-Yeah?

11:40.612 --> 11:42.789
Hey, can you take
a picture of us?

11:42.832 --> 11:44.442
Sure. Why?

11:44.486 --> 11:46.270
Oh, just for
our Facebook page.

11:46.314 --> 11:47.707
Trying to make
your dad jealous, huh?

11:47.750 --> 11:49.099
Pretty much.

11:49.143 --> 11:51.841
Would you just talk to him,
Kendra?
No.

11:51.885 --> 11:53.930
Look, you can stay here
as long as you want,

11:53.974 --> 11:55.627
but you really
belong there.

11:55.671 --> 11:57.934
No. Chale and I
are getting our own place.

11:57.978 --> 11:59.457
Now, come on.
Let's do this.

11:59.501 --> 12:02.112
Okay.

12:02.156 --> 12:03.635
[ Camera shutter clicks ]
There you go.

12:03.679 --> 12:04.985
All right,
what do you say?

12:05.028 --> 12:08.292
You want to crack open
a couple bottles of wine?

12:08.336 --> 12:10.512
I mean, it's Monday,
and it's kinda late.

12:10.555 --> 12:12.949
Oh, right, yeah.
Lost track of time.

12:12.993 --> 12:14.124
Let's have some water.

12:14.168 --> 12:16.126
[ Laughing ] Oh!

12:16.170 --> 12:17.693
We do photograph well
together.

12:17.737 --> 12:19.173
Oh, we do.

12:19.216 --> 12:20.304
[ Both chuckle ]

12:20.348 --> 12:22.002
[ Cork pops ]

12:22.045 --> 12:23.743
What was that?
Vanessa: Nothing.

12:23.786 --> 12:26.136
♪♪

12:26.180 --> 12:28.791
Hey.
You wanna see something sad?

12:28.835 --> 12:31.141
Check out this picture
of Kendra and Chale.

12:31.185 --> 12:32.664
They seem very happy.

12:32.708 --> 12:34.797
It's staged, Guy.

12:34.841 --> 12:36.712
They just posted it
to get to me.

12:36.756 --> 12:38.801
Okay, let me tell you
this story.

12:38.845 --> 12:41.151
My father and brother
once got into a fight

12:41.195 --> 12:42.805
over something
no one remembers.

12:42.849 --> 12:44.981
They didn't speak
for years.

12:45.025 --> 12:47.679
So, finally, my brother
put aside his stubbornness,

12:47.723 --> 12:49.290
and he made the first move.

12:49.333 --> 12:51.553
He walked into my papa's
little cottage,

12:51.596 --> 12:54.164
only to find him dead.

12:54.208 --> 12:56.776
My brother regrets it
to this day.

12:56.819 --> 12:58.821
That smile's so fake.

12:58.865 --> 13:00.780
Uhh!
Hey, where are you?

13:00.823 --> 13:01.824
Uhh! Uhh!

13:01.868 --> 13:04.044
Wait a second.

13:04.087 --> 13:07.003
That's Vanessa's.
Look.

13:07.047 --> 13:09.092
She -- She better not be
letting them stay there.

13:09.136 --> 13:11.051
I told her
not to get involved.

13:11.094 --> 13:13.357
That would be an insane kick
to the nuggets,

13:13.401 --> 13:15.403
but are you sure
it's her place?

13:15.446 --> 13:18.449
Not 100%, but, you know,
I'm gonna find out.

13:18.493 --> 13:20.843
You want me to rent
the apartment next to hers?

13:20.887 --> 13:22.453
You know --
blend in with the community,

13:22.497 --> 13:25.195
establish trust,
and then set up a wiretap?

13:25.239 --> 13:27.023
I'm just gonna
go over there.

13:27.067 --> 13:29.199
Okay.

13:29.243 --> 13:33.464
♪♪

13:33.508 --> 13:35.162
Hey.

13:35.205 --> 13:37.207
Is that Vanessa's place?
Yes.

13:37.251 --> 13:39.296
Aren't you gonna knock?

13:39.340 --> 13:41.821
