about espionage.

13:47.914 --> 13:49.567
I got to be honest.
I don't think you do.

13:49.611 --> 13:51.308
I don't think you even know
what "espionage" means.

13:51.352 --> 13:52.396
Do, too.
Do not.

13:52.440 --> 13:53.484
Do, too.
It means spy.

13:53.528 --> 13:56.009
Oh, no-duh!

13:56.052 --> 13:57.749
You don't knock
on that door.

13:57.793 --> 13:59.012
You come to the neighbor,

13:59.055 --> 14:00.752
and you work your way
out to the patio,

14:00.796 --> 14:01.884
and you peek from there.

14:01.928 --> 14:03.277
Okay, that's not espionage.

14:03.320 --> 14:05.061
That's recon.

14:05.105 --> 14:08.673
I have a feeling youdon't
know what "espionage" means.

14:08.717 --> 14:09.718
Really?
Yeah.

14:09.761 --> 14:10.980
I think I know
what I'm doing, okay?

14:11.024 --> 14:12.286
Been on the force
for 20 years

14:12.329 --> 14:14.070
while you were eating
waffles in Belgium.

14:14.114 --> 14:16.029
Holland.
I'm from Holland.

14:16.072 --> 14:17.552
Just pull the car around,
would you?

14:17.595 --> 14:19.032
Okay.

14:19.075 --> 14:22.296
