I'm the building inspector.

14:34.134 --> 14:36.136
I just got to check
your patio for a second,

14:36.179 --> 14:37.137
if you don't mind.

14:37.180 --> 14:38.660
Go right ahead.
Okay.

14:38.703 --> 14:40.923
I hope Helen
don't get annoyed, okay?

14:40.967 --> 14:43.099
Oh, she'll be fine.
I can sweet-talk her.

14:43.143 --> 14:45.536
[ Both laugh ]

14:45.580 --> 14:47.234
[ Helen growls, barks ]

14:47.277 --> 14:48.713
Helen's a dog!

14:48.757 --> 14:51.803
-Yep, yep.
-Aah!

14:51.847 --> 14:54.067
[ Helen barking, snarling ]

14:55.590 --> 14:56.852
Aah!

14:56.896 --> 14:57.853
[ Shouts indistinctly ]
[ Snarling continues ]

15:03.380 --> 15:05.121
Morning.
Good morning.

15:07.428 --> 15:08.908
Good morning!

15:08.951 --> 15:11.214
-Mm-hmm.
-Oh.

15:11.258 --> 15:12.607
Okay.

15:12.650 --> 15:14.087
Really?
You're not talking to me?

15:14.130 --> 15:15.305
[ Breathes deeply ]

15:15.349 --> 15:16.959
Oh, come on!

15:17.003 --> 15:18.439
Why are you mad at me?

15:18.482 --> 15:20.441
I was almost killed
by a dog last night.

15:20.484 --> 15:22.965
Yeah, because you were
trying to spy on me.

15:23.009 --> 15:24.749
Some people
call it espionage.

15:24.793 --> 15:27.709
But I believe
the correct term is "recon."

15:27.752 --> 15:29.102
Okay.

15:29.145 --> 15:30.233
The only reason I was there

15:30.277 --> 15:31.626
is 'cause you were
harboring my daughter.

15:31.669 --> 15:33.976
Harboring?! What --
She's not a fugitive.

15:34.020 --> 15:36.761
I told you to stay out of this,
Benedict Cumberbatch.

15:36.805 --> 15:38.546
What?

15:38.589 --> 15:40.156
The traitor.

15:40.200 --> 15:42.898
Oh, okay, that's --
Benedict Arnoldis a traitor.

15:42.942 --> 15:44.769
Benedict Cumberbatch
is an actor.

15:44.813 --> 15:47.468
Okay, you know nothing.

15:47.511 --> 15:48.817
Okay?

15:48.860 --> 15:50.906
I can't believe
you went behind my back.

15:50.950 --> 15:53.561
They had
nowhere else to go.

15:53.604 --> 15:55.780
What was
I supposed to say?

15:55.824 --> 15:57.304
Uh, "listen to your father,

15:57.347 --> 15:59.915
for he is wise
in the ways of the world."

15:59.959 --> 16:01.308
Look, she's a sweet kid.

16:01.351 --> 16:03.484
I've known her
since she was born.

16:03.527 --> 16:05.051
Do you know that, last month
when I had the flu,

16:05.094 --> 16:06.269
she just brought me
over soup?

16:06.313 --> 16:07.879
I didn't even ask her.
She just brought it.

16:07.923 --> 16:09.011
I got you soup.

16:09.055 --> 16:10.491
You never got me soup.
I would've.

16:10.534 --> 16:12.145
I would have definitely
done it, but you know what?

16:12.188 --> 16:14.277
They were out of lids.
What -- What am I gonna do?

16:14.321 --> 16:16.279
You want me to drive
in the car with an open soup?

16:16.323 --> 16:18.499
That's literally one of
the leading causes of death.

16:18.542 --> 16:22.068
I'm sorry. I'm not willing
to die for you over open soup.

16:22.111 --> 16:23.895
Okay, y-you know
what your problem is?

16:23.939 --> 16:25.723
And -- And you're not
gonna wanna hear this,

16:25.767 --> 16:28.509
but you don't --
You don't like change.

16:28.552 --> 16:30.032
You don't want Enzo's
to change.

16:30.076 --> 16:31.599
You don't want
your daughter to grow up.

16:31.642 --> 16:33.644
You wanna control
everything.

16:33.688 --> 16:35.646
Yes. Why do you think
I'm going through all of this?

16:35.690 --> 16:38.693
I know, but you're
just pushing her away.

16:38.736 --> 16:41.043
It's like trying
to control mashed potatoes

16:41.087 --> 16:43.176
by holding it
in your hand.

16:43.219 --> 16:45.700
And the more you squeeze
and tighten,

16:45.743 --> 16:48.050
the more it slips
through your fingers.

16:48.094 --> 16:50.183
Wow.

16:50.226 --> 16:52.054
You're thinking about
mashed potatoes now, right?

16:52.098 --> 16:54.056
I am.
Yep.

16:54.100 --> 16:55.405
We're done.

16:56.624 --> 17:00.541
♪♪

17:02.630 --> 17:04.936
Hey, Dad.
I got your text.

17:04.980 --> 17:06.721
What's the emergency?

17:06.764 --> 17:10.333
There's no emergency,
all right?

17:10.377 --> 17:11.595
Grab a spoon.

17:13.336 --> 17:15.469
I got you pistachio.
Your favorite.

17:15.512 --> 17:16.905
