17:16.948 --> 17:18.907
Okay, can we stop arguing
for one second, please?

17:18.950 --> 17:20.082
Honestly.

17:20.126 --> 17:22.041
Fine.

17:22.084 --> 17:25.087
I also got you black cherry
and -- and Moose Tracks.

17:25.131 --> 17:26.567
What's Moose Tracks?

17:26.610 --> 17:30.484
It's fudge and
peanut butter cups in vanilla.

17:30.527 --> 17:32.442
But I've eaten most
of the peanut butter cups,

17:32.486 --> 17:34.879
so unless I missed
a fudge vein,

17:34.923 --> 17:38.100
it's just vanilla now.

17:38.144 --> 17:39.754
So, what do
you wanna talk about?

17:39.797 --> 17:40.972
Listen, I was outta line

17:41.016 --> 17:43.105
trying to control
the whole Enzo's thing

17:43.149 --> 17:47.153
and spying on you
and telling Jack and Sara

17:47.196 --> 17:48.589
they were the only family
I had left.

17:48.632 --> 17:49.807
You said that?

17:49.851 --> 17:50.939
I did.
It got pretty dark.

17:50.982 --> 17:52.201
I'm not...

17:53.550 --> 17:56.814
But the truth is, um...

17:56.858 --> 17:58.120
I miss my little girl,
you know,

17:58.164 --> 18:01.036
and we miss you guys
being in the garage.

18:01.080 --> 18:02.951
I'm not gonna lie.

18:02.994 --> 18:05.301
We miss being there.

18:05.345 --> 18:07.216
And I'm sorry, too.

18:07.260 --> 18:09.000
All right. Oh!

18:09.044 --> 18:11.307
I got you this.

18:11.351 --> 18:13.614
It's a couple grand light
'cause I had to get a dog bite

18:13.657 --> 18:15.268
