but...

18:15.311 --> 18:17.139
Okay, but wait a minute.

18:17.183 --> 18:18.575
How is this
all gonna work?

18:18.619 --> 18:20.447
I'm gonna be
a silent partner, all right?

18:20.490 --> 18:23.754
You and Chale do whatever
