really knows what he's doing.

18:28.063 --> 18:29.978
He's good at this stuff.
I know.

18:30.021 --> 18:32.067
I've held my tongue
long enough.

18:32.111 --> 18:33.416
I got something
to say to you, brother.

18:33.460 --> 18:35.070
All I wanted
was my own beer --

18:35.114 --> 18:36.637
a little legacy
for myself --

18:36.680 --> 18:37.768
but you couldn't let me
have it,

18:37.812 --> 18:39.161
'cause you never
let me have anything.

18:39.205 --> 18:41.076
Well, guess what?
We are done.

18:41.120 --> 18:43.122
You are dead to me.
Dead!

18:44.645 --> 18:46.037
It's back on.
We're buying Enzo's.

18:46.081 --> 18:47.387
Great.
Call you tomorrow.

18:47.430 --> 18:48.431
♪♪

18:54.568 --> 18:56.004
All right, guys.

18:56.047 --> 18:57.658
This is a big moment
for me.

18:57.701 --> 18:59.834
